description*.en: Energy has corresponding intensive (size-independent) properties for pure materials. A corresponding intensive property is specific internal energy, which is energy per mass of substance involved. Specific internal energy is denoted by a lower case u, with dimension of energy per mass (SI unit: joule/kg).
